recision, visualized with a PDF-to-clauses diagram.\n\n\n**Crafting Premium Implementation**\n\nI'm now diving into the implementation phase. I'm focusing on the `app/build/roi/page.tsx` file to incorporate a bespoke interactive narrative. The plan involves adding `activeDept` state for tab management and premium visual elements. I will use Tailwind accents to craft custom slider handles. My goal is to create clean spacing, and to achieve a premium layout. The `editor` is being used to replace the existing implementation with this enhanced version.\n\n\n**Defining Department Details**\n\nI'm now defining the structure for department details. I've created an interface, `DeptDetail`, and a corresponding record `DEPT_DETAILS` to store department-specific information. I'm starting with Finance, defining its title, bottleneck, solution, agent, metrics (with labels, values, and colors), and a brief description. I'll continue to add details for Compliance, Supply Chain, and Legal.\n\n\n**Refining Agent Metrics**\n\nI'm now refining the agent metrics. For \"Risk & Compliance,\" I've fleshed out details for the \"GFF Policy Watchdog,\" including telemetry coverage, incident latency, and manual auditing saved. I'm now adding similar structured details for \"Operations & Logistics,\" focusing on SAP/ERP integration and webhook listeners. My goal is to clearly articulate the value proposition of each department's solution.\n\n\n**Adding Logistics Flow**\n\nI'm now incorporating the \"Operations & Logistics\" details into the interactive diagrams. I've defined the \"Logistics Route Optimizer\" agent. I've also set up the related metrics: \"Transit Overhead Saved,\" \"Pipeline Automation Ratio,\" and \"Average ETA Advantage.\" Finally, I'm building out a description that highlights the agent's ability to streamline route optimization.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T07:21:19.847Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"miqns8zi","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/build/roi/page.tsx","old_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\n\nexport default function ROICalculatorPage() {\n  const [size, setSize] = useState(250);\n  const [hours, setHours] = useState(8);\n  const [rate, setRate] = useState(65);\n  const [invest, setInvest] = useState(35000);\n\n  const annualHours = Math.round(size * hours * 52 * 0.85);\n  const grossSavings = annualHours * rate;\n  const netSavings = Math.max(0, grossSavings - invest);\n  const roi = invest > 0 ? Math.round((netSavings / invest) * 100) : 0;\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Executive Calculator\"\n        title=\"Operational ROI Calculator\"\n        highlightedWord=\"ROI Calculator\"\n        description=\"Quantify structural cost reductions, productivity reclaimed, and net financial ROI of deploying autonomous agent fleets.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-16\">\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          {/* Sliders Control Board */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 space-y-6 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#04060b]\">\n            <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Financial Model Variables</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\"><span>Enterprise Team Size</span><span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{size} Employees</span></div>\n                <input type=\"range\" min=\"10\" max=\"1000\" step=\"10\" value={size} onChange={(e) => setSize(Number(e.target.value))} className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\" />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\"><span>Weekly Process Hours Reclaimed</span><span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{hours} Hours</span></div>\n                <input type=\"range\" min=\"2\" max=\"20\" step=\"1\" value={hours} onChange={(e) => setHours(Number(e.target.value))} className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\" />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\"><span>Blended Hourly Labor Cost</span><span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">${rate}/Hour</span></div>\n                <input type=\"range\" min=\"25\" max=\"150\" step=\"5\" value={rate} onChange={(e) => setRate(Number(e.target.value))} className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\" />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\"><span>Annual Licensing & Integration</span><span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">${invest.toLocaleString()}</span></div>\n                <input type=\"range\" min=\"15000\" max=\"150000\" step=\"5000\" value={invest} onChange={(e) => setInvest(Number(e.target.value))} className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Dynamic Financial Outputs */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n            <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Annual Labor Saved</span>\n              <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-1\">{annualHours.toLocaleString()} Hrs</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Gross Productivity Value</span>\n              <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#00FF9D] mt-1\">${grossSavings.toLocaleString()}</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Net Annual Cost Savings</span>\n              <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#009DFF] mt-1\">${netSavings.toLocaleString()}</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Projected Investment ROI</span>\n              <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#E4000F] mt-1\">{roi}%</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"col-span-2 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Model Allocation Guidelines</span>\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-[11px] text-white/60 font-light\">\n                <div><span className=\"font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">15%</span> Compute cost</div>\n                <div><span className=\"font-bold text-[#00FF9D]\">45%</span> Compliance audits</div>\n                <div><span className=\"font-bold text-white\">40%</span> Active work-speed</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <PremiumCTA />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\n\ntype DeptKey = \"finance\" | \"compliance\" | \"supply\" | \"legal\";\n\ninterface DeptDetail {\n  title: string;\n  bottleneck: string;\n  solution: string;\n  agent: string;\n  metrics: { label: string; value: string; color: string }[];\n  description: string;\n}\n\nconst DEPT_DETAILS: Record<DeptKey, DeptDetail> = {\n  finance: {\n    title: \"Finance & Auditing\",\n    bottleneck: \"Manual ledger reconciliation and multi-ledger transaction anomaly sweeps are retrospectively audited, taking 40+ hours per week.\",\n    solution: \"Deploy Autonomous Consensus Nodes to run real-time checks on transaction schemas.\",\n    agent: \"AS-09 Consensus Auditor\",\n    metrics: [\n      { label: \"Audit Accuracy Rate\", value: \"99.98%\", color: \"#00FF9D\" },\n      { label: \"Deployment Horizon\", value: \"14 Days\", color: \"#009DFF\" },\n      { label: \"Weekly Labor Freed\", value: \"32 Hours\", color: \"#9D00FF\" }\n    ],\n    description: \"The AS-09 Auditor maps database mirrors directly inside private subnets, performing cryptographically secure checksum verification on high-throughput ledgers with absolute zero retention.\"\n  },\n  compliance: {\n    title: \"Risk & Compliance\",\n    bottleneck: \"Tracking cloud infrastructure configuration drift and mapping policies to SOC2 frameworks requires tedious manual telemetry logs.\",\n    solution: \"Establish localized guardrail interceptors that scan resource parameters continuously.\",\n    agent: \"GFF Policy Watchdog\",\n    metrics: [\n      { label: \"Telemetry Coverage\", value: \"100.0%\", color: \"#00FF9D\" },\n      { label: \"Incident Latency\", value: \"< 5 Sec\", color: \"#009DFF\" },\n      { label: \"Manual Auditing Saved\", value: \"85%\", color: \"#E4000F\" }\n    ],\n    description: \"Our compliance agents intercept active VPC configurations, blocking unauthorised policy drift and piping structured telemetry directly to high-fidelity audit reports.\"\n  },\n  supply: {\n    title: \"Operations & Logistics\",\n    bottleneck: \"SAP ERP container routing updates and port logistics exceptions are managed via manual messaging and retrospective spreadsheets.\",\n    solution: \"Integrate SAP/ERP webhook listeners that model route logistics dynamically.\",\n    agent: \"Logistics Route Optimizer\",\n    metrics: [\n      { label: \"Transit Overhead Saved\", value: \"22.4%\", color: \"#00FF9D\" },\n      { label: \"Pipeline Automation Ratio\", value: \"88.0%\", color: \"#009DFF\" },\n      { label: \"Average ETA Advantage\", value: \"18 Hrs\", color: \"#9D00FF\" }\n    ],\n    description: \"This agent operates directly on logistic container pipelines, autonomously evaluating route pricing, sea-port traffic patterns, and overland cargo delays to minimize transit times.\"\n  },\n  legal: {\n    title: \"Legal & SOW Drafting\",\n    bottleneck: \"Drafting Statements of Work and validating customized multi-tenant SLA clauses takes up to 7 business days per draft.\",\n    solution: \"Run secure PDF model parser enclaves to pre-screen clauses against company standards.\",\n    agent: \"Sovereign NDA Parser\",\n    metrics: [\n      { label: \"Drafting Time Saved\", value: \"90.0%\", color: \"#00FF9D\" },\n      { label: \"Precision Rate\", value: \"99.5%\", color: \"#009DFF\" },\n      { label: \"Average Turnaround\", value: \"15 Min\", color: \"#E4000F\" }\n    ],\n    description: \"The NDA Parser isolates client agreements in single-tenant hardware blocks, scanning and highlighting non-standard terms, risk-shifting covenants, and liability thresholds.\"\n  }\n};\n\nexport default function ROICalculatorPage() {\n  const [size, setSize] = useState(250);\n  const [hours, setHours] = useState(8);\n  const [rate, setRate] = useState(65);\n  const [invest, setInvest] = useState(35000);\n  const [activeDept, setActiveDept] = useState<DeptKey>(\"finance\");\n\n  const annualHours = Math.round(size * hours * 52 * 0.85);\n  const grossSavings = annualHours * rate;\n  const netSavings = Math.max(0, grossSavings - invest);\n  const roi = invest > 0 ? Math.round((netSavings / invest) * 100) : 0;\n\n  const currentDept = DEPT_DETAILS[activeDept];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Executive Calculator\"\n        title=\"Operational ROI Calculator\"\n        highlightedWord=\"ROI Calculator\"\n        description=\"Quantify structural cost reductions, productivity reclaimed, and net financial ROI of deploying autonomous agent fleets.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-16\">\n        {/* Core Financial Matrix */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          {/* Sliders Control Board */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 space-y-6 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#04060b]\">\n            <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] uppercase tracking-wider block\">VARIABLE CONSOLE</span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Financial Model Variables</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\">\n                  <span>Enterprise Team Size</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold font-mono\">{size} Employees</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"10\"\n                  max=\"1000\"\n                  step=\"10\"\n                  value={size}\n                  onChange={(e) => setSize(Number(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F] cursor-pointer\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\">\n                  <span>Weekly Process Hours Reclaimed per Employee</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold font-mono\">{hours} Hours</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"2\"\n                  max=\"20\"\n                  step=\"1\"\n                  value={hours}\n                  onChange={(e) => setHours(Number(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F] cursor-pointer\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\">\n                  <span>Blended Hourly Labor Cost</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold font-mono\">${rate}/Hour</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"25\"\n                  max=\"150\"\n                  step=\"5\"\n                  value={rate}\n                  onChange={(e) => setRate(Number(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F] cursor-pointer\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs text-white/80\">\n                  <span>Annual Licensing & Integration Cost</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#E4000F] font-bold font-mono\">${invest.toLocaleString()}</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"15000\"\n                  max=\"150000\"\n                  step=\"5000\"\n                  value={invest}\n                  onChange={(e) => setInvest(Number(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F] cursor-pointer\"\n                />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Dynamic Financial Outputs */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Annual Labor Saved</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mt-2 font-mono\">{annualHours.toLocaleString()} Hrs</span>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-4 bottom-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition\">\n                <svg className=\"w-8 h-8 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" />\n                </svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Gross Productivity Value</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#00FF9D] mt-2 font-mono\">${grossSavings.toLocaleString()}</span>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-4 bottom-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition\">\n                <svg className=\"w-8 h-8 text-[#00FF9D]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" />\n                </svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Net Annual Cost Savings</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#009DFF] mt-2 font-mono\">${netSavings.toLocaleString()}</span>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-4 bottom-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition\">\n                <svg className=\"w-8 h-8 text-[#009DFF]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\" />\n                </svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050101] flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Projected Investment ROI</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#E4000F] mt-2 font-mono\">{roi}%</span>\n              <div className=\"absolute right-4 bottom-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition\">\n                <svg className=\"w-8 h-8 text-[#E4000F]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2z\" />\n                </svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"col-span-2 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 space-y-3\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Model Allocation Guidelines</span>\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-xs text-white/60 font-light\">\n                <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40\">\n                  <span className=\"font-bold text-[#009DFF] font-mono block text-sm\">15%</span> \n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50\">Compute overhead</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40\">\n                  <span className=\"font-bold text-[#00FF9D] font-mono block text-sm\">45%</span> \n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50\">Compliance audits</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40\">\n                  <span className=\"font-bold text-white font-mono block text-sm\">40%</span> \n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50\">Active execution speed</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Operational Bottlenecks & Impact Dashboard */}\n        <div className=\"border border-white/5 bg-[#030408] rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-10 space-y-8\">\n          <div className=\"text-center space-y-2\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase tracking-widest block\">OPERATIONAL BLUEPRINT</span>\n            <h3 className=\"text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Departmental Impact Matrix</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-white/60 text-xs font-light max-w-[500px] mx-auto\">See exactly where sovereign agent topologies remove process delays and scale operations.</p>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Department Selector Tabs */}\n          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n            {(Object.keys(DEPT_DETAILS) as DeptKey[]).map((key) => (\n              <button\n                key={key}\n                onClick={() => setActiveDept(key)}\n                className={`px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-lg border transition ${\n                  activeDept === key\n                    ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]/30\"\n                    : \"bg-white/[0.01] text-white/50 border-white/5 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                {DEPT_DETAILS[key].title}\n              </button>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Tab Details */}\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center pt-2\">\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-6\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest block\">THE CHALLENGE</span>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">{currentDept.bottleneck}</p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 space-y-3\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-widest\">GFF AUTONOMOUS NODE</span>\n                    <h4 className=\"text-base font-bold text-white\">{currentDept.agent}</h4>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/5 px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-emerald-500/10 uppercase font-semibold\">ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">{currentDept.description}</p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                {currentDept.metrics.map((m, idx) => (\n                  <div key={idx} className=\"p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 text-center\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block mb-1\">{m.label}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-lg font-bold font-mono\" style={{ color: m.color }}>{m.value}</span>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Custom SVG Architecture Graphics */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex justify-center items-center bg-black/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 min-h-[280px]\">\n              {activeDept === \"finance\" && (\n                <svg className=\"w-full max-w-[280px] h-auto\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\" fill=\"none\">\n                  {/* Database Node */}\n                  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"80\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                  <text x=\"40\" y=\"105\" fill=\"#009DFF\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">DB IN</text>\n                  \n                  {/* Consensus Auditor */}\n                  <rect x=\"140\" y=\"80\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                  <text x=\"160\" y=\"105\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">AS-09</text>\n                  \n                  {/* Connecting lines */}\n                  <path d=\"M60 100 H140\" stroke=\"white\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeDasharray=\"4 4\" strokeOpacity=\"0.4\" />\n                  <path d=\"M60 100 H140\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeDasharray=\"12 40\" strokeDashoffset=\"10\">\n                    <animate attributeName=\"stroke-dashoffset\" values=\"40;0\" dur=\"2s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                  </path>\n                  \n                  {/* Ledger blocks */}\n                  <rect x=\"90\" y=\"45\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                  <rect x=\"90\" y=\"135\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                  <path d=\"M100 60 V80 M100 120 V135\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                </svg>\n              )}\n\n              {activeDept === \"compliance\" && (\n                <svg className=\"w-full max-w-[280px] h-auto\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\" fill=\"none\">\n                  {/* Outer Radar Loop */}\n                  <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"100\" r=\"70\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"3 3\" strokeOpacity=\"0.3\" />\n                  <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"100\" r=\"50\" stroke=\"#9D00FF\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" />\n                  \n                  {/* Center Node */}\n                  <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"100\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"2\" />\n                  <text x=\"100\" y=\"103\" fill=\"#00FF9D\" fontSize=\"8\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fontWeight=\"bold\">SECURE</text>\n                  \n                  {/* Interactive Sweep Radar line */}\n                  <line x1=\"100\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"50\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeOpacity=\"0.7\">\n                    <animateTransform attributeName=\"transform\" type=\"rotate\" from=\"0 100 100\" to=\"360 100 100\" dur=\"4s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                  </line>\n\n                  {/* Telemetry Dots */}\n                  <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"80\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#9D00FF\" />\n                  <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"120\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#E4000F\" />\n                  <circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"150\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#009DFF\" />\n                </svg>\n              )}\n\n              {activeDept === \"supply\" && (\n                <svg className=\"w-full max-w-[280px] h-auto\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\" fill=\"none\">\n                  {/* Core Route Nodes */}\n                  <circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"60\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                  <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"70\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                  <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"140\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#04060b\" stroke=\"#00FF9D\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                  \n                  {/* Intersecting path lines */}\n                  <path d=\"M46 62 L94 138\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                  <path d=\"M154 72 L106 138\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                  <path d=\"M46 60 H154\" stroke=\"white\" strokeOpacity=\"0.1\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n                  \n                  {/* Container flow animation */}\n                  <circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"60\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#00FF9D\">\n                    <animate attributeName=\"cx\" values=\"40;100;40\" dur=\"3s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                    <animate attributeName=\"cy\" values=\"60;140;60\" dur=\"3s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                  </circle>\n                  <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#009DFF\">\n                    <animate attributeName=\"cx\" values=\"160;100;160\" dur=\"4s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                    <animate attributeName=\"cy\" values=\"70;140;70\" dur=\"4s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n                  </circle>\n                  \n                  <text x=\"40\" y=\"48\" fill=\"white\" fillOpacity=\"0.6\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">POR